# USAGE GUIDE 🚀
Welcome to **Vibe Check** 😎
This guide explains how to use the application after installation.

---

# 🌐 Launch the App
Make sure both frontend and backend servers are running.
Open your browser and visit:
```bash
http://localhost:5173
```

---

# 🔐 Step 1: Create Account / Login
When the app opens:
✅ New users can create an account
✅ Existing users can log in securely
Authentication is powered by **Firebase**.

---

# 🧠 Step 2: Enter Your Mood
After login, you will see the mood input section.
Type how you are feeling, for example:
```text 
Ma boht udaas hn.
```
Then click:
✅ Enter
---

# 🤖 Step 3: Sentiment Analysis
The system analyzes your text using AI and detects mood such as:

* 😊 Happy
* 😔 Sad
* 😤 Angry
* 😓 Stressed
* 😐 Neutral
* 💪 Motivated

---

# 💡 Step 4: Get Personalized Recommendations
Based on your detected mood, Vibe Check suggests:
* 🌿 Relaxation tips
* 🏃 Healthy activities
* 📖 Positive habits
* 🎯 Productivity ideas
* 💬 Motivation support
---

# 😂 Step 5: Enjoy Meme Suggestions
To lighten your mood, the app provides fun meme content.
This feature is designed to add humor and reduce stress.

---

# 🎵📚🎬 Step 6: Explore Entertainment Picks
Users also receive recommendations such as:
## 🎵 Music
Songs matching your mood.
## 📚 Books
Interesting books based on emotional state.
## 🎬 Movies
Feel-good or mood-matching movies.

---

# 👤 Step 7: Manage Session
Users can:
✅ Logout securely
✅ Login anytime again

---
# 💡 Best Ways to Use Vibe Check
* Start your morning mood check 🌅
* Use when stressed during study/work 📚
* Discover uplifting content 🎶
* Relax with memes 😂
* Improve emotional awareness 🧠
---

